Roger Gurnani



Mr. Roger Gurnani is Chief Information & Technology Architect, EVP at Verizon Communications, Inc. Mr. Gurnani was previously employed as Senior Vice President-New Product Development by Verizon Wireless, Inc., Chief Information Officer & Vice President by Bell Atlantic Mobile, Chief Information Officer & Vice President by GTE Corp., and Chief Information Officer & Vice President by Vodafone AirTouch Plc. He received his undergraduate degree from Auburn University and a graduate degree from Auburn University.



